Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.21,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.82,0:00:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.27,0:00:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.32,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.33,0:01:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.40,0:01:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,你要把伊吹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.63,0:01:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳也跟妳爸爸一起回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,你為什麼不接受呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.40,0:01:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,我非常渴望這封介紹信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.57,0:01:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的無法收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕自己會這樣隨波逐流下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就業的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.75,0:01:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這是我自己的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.99,0:02:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#78這是秘密!\N五代的打工奮鬥記!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.27,0:02:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-賴皮,一對一根本打不贏…\N-大哥哥的身體比較大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.90,0:02:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那你們一起上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.68,0:02:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油,加油…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我錄取了,我錄取了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被陽炎產業錄取了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.46,0:02:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神部長的介紹信真的很有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的收下那封介紹信了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧,妳連這種事都不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-人家真的不知道嘛\N-真是夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹在家的感覺果然很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.53,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,這一個月真是漫長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.14,0:03:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,五代他為什麼說\N不要那封介紹信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道,我才懶得理那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的關係\N給我添了多少麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也應該很清楚才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了,這種時候不要談他的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.89,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,他說要自己決定\N這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能覺得我對他是個負擔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.83,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師可能覺得很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為八神很專情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.94,0:04:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去找他確認一下如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.44,0:04:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他現在很後悔\N自己說出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.05,0:04:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,妳連離家出走都做了\N再去找他確認一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.56,0:04:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好喝的啤酒\N是考上大學以來的第二次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是敗給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然硬向八神部長\N要來那封介紹信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉,我可是拼了命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯過這種大好機會\N不會有第二次了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你,你是不是後悔了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事後恨我,我也不管你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也才不管你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一那家公司又倒閉了\N哭死了我也不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.56,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎產業,聽起來就像是一家\N快要消失的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.53,0:05:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,我是開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神她爸爸也說過了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是慎重選擇的\N絕對不會倒閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還保證呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.75,0:05:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,今晚要喝個痛快\N全部我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.16,0:05:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥,啤酒儘管拿過來\N再來個五、六瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.16,0:05:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有燒酒加檸檬,烏龍茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草莓,番茄,哈蜜瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蘋果,梅子,柳橙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小黃瓜,酪梨,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,開一瓶威士忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥,再來一瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在幹嘛,快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,馬上來,馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.41,0:06:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說阪本找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以跑去喝酒\N今晚說不定不回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,他還真悠哉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨,歡迎再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,再去喝一家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要喝一家啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是去酒家啦,酒家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有認識的人在那裡工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他幫我們\N介紹幾個漂亮美眉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很喜歡“介紹”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,慶祝大學生找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡再來四瓶啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外加一盤花枝拼盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.23,0:07:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,帥哥,你好大方喔\N你會出人頭地喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的囉\N這傢伙的後台可是很有力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果昨天晚上沒回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.83,0:07:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要幫阪本慶祝找到工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他有時間幫別人慶祝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太悠哉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟這種男人結婚會吃苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.78,0:08:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會吃苦我是不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.38,0:08:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作是一輩子的事\N還是慢慢找比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.12,0:08:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還慢慢找?都已經10月了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初應該收下那封介紹信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那封介紹信\N就算沒優點的五代也能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.76,0:08:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代他也很努力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門沒鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,臭死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還在睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!給我起來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.24,0:09:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還敢問!\N你要睡到什麼時候!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯岡先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,你這傢伙真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點起來準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.58,0:09:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我裝蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.39,0:09:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是說好了嗎\N錢不夠的部分用打工來償還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎?我不記得有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.26,0:09:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我來這一套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點,快點\N不用換衣服了,穿這樣就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲到?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.14,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎?當然是去幼稚園啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,你不要給我說夢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,結果怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他請假沒來上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,人家特地來找他耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.37,0:10:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是去找工作了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.44,0:10:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道,好像沒有打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是生病了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生車禍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被綁架了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.72,0:10:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好,在酒錢還清之前\N我會好好鍛鍊你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先做好心理準備喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是,請多指教\N-是,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太小聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-請多指教!\N-請多指教!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.40,0:10:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,接客的時候\N要面帶開朗笑容,口齒清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說說看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,接客的時候\N要面帶開朗笑容,口齒清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,這句話要牢牢記住喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.18,0:10:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們公司的社訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來到公司外面\N展開實地訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司外面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實地訓練?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,這位老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有折價優待\N可以享受極樂氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要進來看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.84,0:11:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲,不要這麼說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是出來找樂子的,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.67,0:11:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來,帶兩位裡面坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,你們兩個也試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-啊?\N-啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.32,0:11:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊你個頭啦,快去試試看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨頭笨腦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能照著他的話做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?出聲拉客啊,出聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.33,0:11:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間酒家正在打折優待…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這間酒家,正在打折優待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找情侶幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.41,0:12:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你的態度幹嘛陰沈沈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.52,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼\N你看看阪本,他就做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,要不要進來坐一坐啊\N有漂亮的美眉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲,不要走嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,不用拉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,阪本,這位是常客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.80,0:12:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好您好,陽炎產業的總經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.31,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來來,請進請進\N麗莎在等你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.98,0:12:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎產業不就是你要去的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.15,0:12:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不妙吧,聽說他是常客耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.53,0:12:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我把五代放在這裡抵債
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,給我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也想溜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作找得還順利嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.91,0:13:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好\N今天也想去就職課看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,真的很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很累的樣子\N不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.95,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事,我不要緊的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.50,0:14:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我明明沒必要說謊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八…八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.70,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,你不是生病啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.53,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我昨天去幼稚園\N你請假沒上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.77,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,不過妳看\N我沒生病好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,你找工作還順利嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉,我沒什麼時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有很重要的事要去辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.13,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那改天再聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.93,0:15:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.70,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.28,0:15:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他真的覺得我是個負擔嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.46,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接客的時候\N要面帶開朗笑容,口齒清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接客的時候\N要面帶開朗笑容,口齒清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,今天也提起精神,好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,請進請進\N折價大優待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,請進請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,老闆\N漂亮的美眉在等著你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.71,0:15:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在折價大優待\N喝到飽,吃到飽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.02,0:15:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你也表現得很不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.85,0:16:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?\N因為我得連阪本的份一起努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還談不上了不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經自暴自棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,有年輕漂亮的美眉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在喝酒唱歌都超便宜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,這位老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.83,0:16:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛逃走\N快點帶他進去,帶他進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.43,0:16:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請帶我進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你是五代的鄰居啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要好好服務一下才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看是要吃水果還是開整瓶酒\N儘管叫沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.07,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正五代請客嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託,我幾時說過要請客了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你突然叫她幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.59,0:17:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒去找工作\N跑來酒家打工的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道要我告訴她嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.06,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來,再拿五、六瓶酒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.63,0:17:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝到打烊為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.07,0:17:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哇,好棒喔\N-我可以叫水果切盤嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你答應我的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能告訴管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.82,0:17:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你煩不煩啊\N難道你不相信我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓,開門小聲一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.64,0:18:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你偷偷摸摸在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧\N絕對不能告訴管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.58,0:18:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.02,0:18:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一起回來啊\N真是稀奇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,因為五代在酒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-四谷!\N-魚子醬真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.73,0:18:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喝醉了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋,居然醉成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,上樓去吧,上樓去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.84,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天去就職課問得怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.21,0:18:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請放心,他等於找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是餐飲服務業,對不對?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,睡覺去,睡覺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我一起睡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡扯什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是找工作找得不順利\N所以沒有臉見八神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像很想擺脫八神\N情況不妙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管別人怎麼說都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正八神一定要看到\N五代老師順利就業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則她是不會放手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好專情喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,快來啊快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只限今天特別大優待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,現在折價大優待\N可以享受極樂氣氛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?可以喝免費的酒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.74,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我有朋友在這裡工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,那不是五代嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,這跟我們說好的不一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧,我沒有跟管理員\N透露隻字片語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.23,0:20:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,真的可以\N從你的薪水裡扣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也來喝嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.47,0:20:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知不知道這是誰出的錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.01,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美小姐,朱美小姐\N請轉檯至六號桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.92,0:20:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳幾歲了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.92,0:20:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,17歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.02,0:20:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我才是朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.86,0:20:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這套制服好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想穿穿看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳穿了一定很好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.30,0:20:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我也來這裡工作好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.77,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.04,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.94,0:20:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,竟然全來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把這件事向管理員說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.29,0:21:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我還跟她說\N我是出門去找工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.93,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,謝謝你的招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.96,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要早點回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事絕對不能告訴管理員喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.81,0:21:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便幫你敷衍一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最不會敷衍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.88,0:21:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我也不太會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了\N該說的時候我自己會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣我們會過意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.02,0:21:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛,每晚都讓他請客\N多不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們每晚都想來勒索我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.49,0:21:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,你怎麼說得這麼難聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.03,0:21:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我們已經上了同一條船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.17,0:21:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.94,0:21:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.01,0:21:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚沒跟五代一起回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.61,0:22:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶\N他可能忙著到處找工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.68,0:22:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭上綁著一條黃帶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.32,0:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.12,0:22:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來來,管理員也來喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.66,0:22:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐啊,坐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.26,0:22:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是坐在這裡喝酒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.96,0:22:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係\N大家來祝五代順利就業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.10,0:22:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,快來啊快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.04,0:22:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃到飽,喝到飽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.61,0:22:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美小姐,朱美小姐\N請轉檯至六號桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.91,0:22:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.16,0:22:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.79,0:22:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我工作一向都是很認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.26,0:22:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我就這麼倒楣\N老是碰到這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.67,0:22:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.97,0:22:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼認為吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.08,0:23:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.82,0:23:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝,一共兩千八百塊錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.59,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢…錢不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.43,0:23:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,快來啊快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.13,0:23:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃又便宜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.60,0:23:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,過來嚐嚐看吧\N好吃的黑輪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.10,0:23:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你蠻厲害的嘛\N還剩五百塊,好好加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.41,0:23:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別看我這樣\N我可是這方面的專家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.48,0:23:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,那位老闆\N快來吃好吃的黑輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.28,0:23:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來啊,快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.45,0:23:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的黑輪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.25,0:23:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來吃啊,快來吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,老闆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.06,0:23:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚園的工作被炒魷魚了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.83,0:23:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,頂級的愛情便當呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.43,0:23:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪裡吃呢?用什麼表情吃呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.27,0:23:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像個男子漢從實招來吧\N五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.77,0:24:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.30,0:24:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「響子對不起!\N含淚的愛妻便當?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.41,0:24:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,酒家的工作不要辭掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.14,0:24:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.82,0:24:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.05,0:24:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.03,0:24:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.33,0:24:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.41,0:24:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.11,0:24:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.98,0:24:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.69,0:24:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.96,0:25:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.87,0:25:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.84,0:25:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.28,0:25:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.55,0:25:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.89,0:25:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
